CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper January 12, 1946, pg. 21, reads: "Venison Party - Johnny Craig surprised his friends with a venison party at Crawford Grill No. 1 this week.  Johnny killed a deer on his last hunting trip, and this is the result of his marksmanship. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group, possibly including Johnny Craig, Robert E. "Pappy" Williams second on left, and Johnny Black front right, gathered around dining tables for venison party in Rumpus Room of Crawford Grill No. 1
